[CBM] Appleseed XIII 1-13 Complete (Dual Audio) [DVDRip-480p-8bit]

The world, devastated by a long global conflict, is ruled from the vast city of Olympus
by the General Administration Agency. This Agency is run by human-hybrid clones known as
Bioroid, made from the genes of the best and brightest.

Former Los Angeles S.W.A.T. officer Deunan Knute and her cyborg partner Briareos,
both become residents of Olympus after being scouted by ES.W.A.T., a special counter-terrorist
division of the Global Police.

One such terrorist group which they fight is the Human Liberation Front, which attacked Olympus
in the midst of the launch of the Ark Program, a plan to entrust the future of humanity to Bioroids.
However, subsequent investigations will reveal that someone else had been manipulating the Front from
behind the scenes.
